name: I believe I can fly - Elon Musk 2017
description: hello i am Ayna (mirror).  I am interested in street art.  I did 4 works of Elon Musk in this series.  you see one of them.  I did this job in 2017 to show our love and respect to Elon.  I hope it will be a good motivation for you too.  I will share these works in digital form in the future. If you are curious about my other works, you can check out @aynaofficial on Instagram.
